---
title: Lemon-Garlic Sugar Snap Peas, Broccoli and Mushrooms Serves 6 | with Spiced Almonds
description: The vibrant colour of the ingredients in this dish remain throughout the cooking process, making the end result a visual treat. Garlic spread and pops of lemon really bring the flavour, and spiced nuts sprinkled on top add an elegant, festive  touch.

The ingredients and nutritional values listed below are based on 6 servings.

Ingredients: Sugar snap peas • Broccoli • Mushroom mix (cremini mushrooms, white mushrooms, oyster mushrooms) • Red onion • Lemon • Garlic spread (margarine (soybean oil, water, modified palm and palm kernel oils, salt, vegetable monoglycerides, soy lecithin, potassium sorbate, natural flavour, citric acid, annatto and turmeric, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D2), garlic, onion powder, water, salt, vegetable mono and diglycerides, maltodextrin, citric acid, parsley, natural flavour, xanthan gum, potassium sorbate, natural colour, vitamin E) (soy) • Almonds • Worcestershire sauce (water, sugars (sugar, fancy molasses), worcestershire sauce concentrate (vinegar, blackstrap molasses, glucose, water, caramel, garlic powder, sugar, spices, tamarind, natural flavour), vinegar, salt, spices, natural flavour, potassium sorbate) • Zesty garlic blend (granulated garlic, cornmeal, salt, dehydrated red bell pepper flakes, spices, sugar, herbs, canola oil, silicon dioxide, citric acid) (sulphites).
